osphere by the disc matter and by the\nnon-dipole shape of the magnetic field lines of the external magnetosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Mar 2013 18:09:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
