he\nM(3,p) Virasoro minimal models that has been considered previously, using\nresults from the literature. We exhibit the Hamiltonians for the first few\ncases of these. The techniques we introduce can be applied in numerous examples\nother than those considered here.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Mar 2013 19:44:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Jun 2013 22:34:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2013 13:40:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-04"}
